## Architecture

### System Overview

```
User Application
       ↓
AgentManager (Orchestrator)
       ↓
Agent (Router-Evaluator-Reflector)
       ├─ MASGenerativeModel (LLM + Memory)
       ├─ Tool Executor (static tools + ToolRegistry fallback)
       ├─ ToolRegistry (dynamic tool discovery)
       └─ State Manager
       ↓
Memory System
       ├─ LongTermMemory
       ├─ Redis/Qdrant Backend
       └─ Embedding Model
```

**See [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ARCHITECTURE.md) for detailed architecture.**

